data.description: Rarely available, 4 bed, 2.5 bath home with upgrades in the Sweetbriar section of Barefoot Resort. This home is currently the lowest priced home in Barefoot Landing, price per heated square foot!  This home comes complete with updated floors, kitchen countertops, appliances, bathroom vanities and a large fenced backyard this 2,400 heated square foot home is turnkey and priced to sell. Enjoy everything that Barefoot Resort has to offer including the private 3 story beachfront cabana, salt water pools, tennis, pickle ball, basketball, boating, golf and private security with one of the lowest HOA fees in the area.  The home layout provides the main suite on the first level with the remaining 3 bedrooms upstairs.
